{"tid":1650753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蛋糕女道唔道歉唔重要，呢個係個人人格問題，但手足或者同路人以後都唔好再做","createTime":"2019-10-13T06:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T19:21:02.000Z","uid":259713,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"74c06899feb33664c268ba57f49036f332966a5c","tid":1650753,"uid":259713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:19:57.000Z","msg":"其實之前818事件已經講左一次，太子站算係靈堂，亦算係戰場，唔好係戰場上慶祝。<br />\n同樣既事唔可以再有人犯，手足或者同路人以後唔好再做呢樣野，現場人士亦有義務叫走佢地<br />\n<br />\n各位請今日開始繼續推行動post，集中訴求，同埋所有黑警事件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsh8pnn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzsh8pnn.jpg&h=71a610c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvQ6a2q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvQ6a2q.png&h=e1442df2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰，不分化！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致蛋糕女<br />\n<br />\n　　如果你係手足，你就應該道歉，但我唔會強逼你咁做，因為呢個將會係決定你人格既問題。<br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴既其中一位粉絲攬炒派上"},{"pid":"66de11d0252afb531ebd9dd29ae0652960efd447","tid":1650753,"uid":42182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"繼續專心抗爭"},{"pid":"3bcc89b0799db84b80e6fad4b6ac8861c2baa68c","tid":1650753,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:28:58.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"de47707aac7bfedf201d76b25040b3914d3069fe","tid":1650753,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"人地未道咩?"},{"pid":"6e11d3b7cc410b7be6605a5efe80dc681e42a3d6","tid":1650753,"uid":259713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de47707aac7bfedf201d76b25040b3914d3069fe","tid":1650753,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"人地未道咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:35:06.000Z","msg":"小弟無追咁貼蛋糕女，我只睇開行動post同埋懷疑被自殺個案重要d，<br />\n只係我見到大家係到講緊，我先有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal